			<div class="content" id="post-content-915875">
									

<p>What I don't exactly understand is how you can condition the brain to respond to changes in the OFC neurochemistry. I gather that the researchers would try to look for elevated serotonin levels as the reward system is activated, but that could result in too many false positives.</p>
